me.jamiemansfield.lorenz.io.writer

Class MappingsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.jamiemansfield.lorenz.io.writer.MappingsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CSrgWriter, SrgWriter, TSrgWriter

    public abstract class MappingsWriter
extends Object
implements Closeable
    Represents a writer, that is capable of writing de-obfuscation mappings to a PrintWriter. Each mappings writer will be designed for a specific mapping format, and intended to be used with try-for-resources.
    See Also:
    SrgWriter
